New Generation in Design - Works of German Architect and Interior Designers
Verlagshaus Braun, Berlin | ISBN: 9812451617 | 2004 | PDF | 315 Pages | 24 MB


INTERIOR DESIGN in its everyday presence reflects the changing demands human beings make on their environment. Well-made interiors reveal the architecture qualities of a building, giving them a finely honed setting of light, shapes and textures That is the high art of interior design.
